{"title":"湛江行","authors":["高士其湛"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":3,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"湛江行（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高士其湛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湛江好，好湛江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色城市像花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少游客向往着你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少诗人为你歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹤地水库工程大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拦腰斩断九州江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红色青年干劲高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开山劈岭凿河床。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥上水漕灌田地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥下车马任奔驰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年运河水长流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻粮薯蔗庆丰收。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除尽水害驱旱魔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征服自然奏凯歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堵海长堤意志坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定把沧海变良田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热带作物花盛开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡鸭成群猪牛壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社放光芒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷州建设多辉煌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访湖光岩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山间有一湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖光映岩壁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唐代立庙宇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林荫蔽天日。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佛像殊庄严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人爱古迹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万籁寂无声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"休养亦胜地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1962年3月8日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}